request.description:
Get dashboard overview with stats and recent activity.

**Requires**: Authentication

**Success Response (200)**:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "user": {
    "firstName": "Ahmed",
    "lastName": "Khan",
    "phoneNumber": "923001234567"
  },
  "stats": {
    "totalLessonPlans": 12,
    "totalCoachingSessions": 3
  },
  "recentLessonPlans": [
    {
      "id": "uuid",
      "title": "Photosynthesis Lesson",
      "created_at": "2025-01-15T10:30:00Z",
      "content_type": "lesson_plan",
      "gamma_url": "https://gamma.app/..."
    }
  ],
  "recentCoachingSession": {
    "id": "uuid",
    "date": "2025-01-14T14:00:00Z",
    "score": 87,
    "maxScore": 118
  }
}
```

**Mobile Optimization**: Includes only last 3 lesson plans and 1 coaching session for fast load.

Get coaching score trends and analytics.

**Requires**: Authentication

**Success Response (200)**:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "analytics": {
    "overallScoreTrend": [
      {
        "date": "2025-01-10T10:00:00Z",
        "score": 82,
        "percentage": 69.5
      },
      {
        "date": "2025-01-14T14:00:00Z",
        "score": 87,
        "percentage": 73.7
      }
    ],
    "goalAreaBreakdown": [
      {
        "name": "Formative Assessment",
        "score": 15,
        "maxScore": 20,
        "percentage": 75.0
      },
      {
        "name": "Student Engagement",
        "score": 14,
        "maxScore": 20,
        "percentage": 70.0
      }
    ],
    "insights": {
      "totalSessions": 3,
      "averageScore": 84.3,
      "improvement": 5.0,
      "bestGoalArea": "Formative Assessment",
      "focusArea": "Debrief & Reflection"
    }
  }
}
```

**Mobile Optimization**: Data formatted for ApexCharts (line and bar charts).

**Empty State**: Returns empty arrays if no coaching sessions completed.
